"{\"uid\": \"rte.ie-news-ireland-2024-0808-1464043-olympic-homecoming\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Ireland's Olympic heroes are to be honoured at a public homecoming event in Dublin on Monday afternoon.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 103, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 7, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999999999988631, \"rank\": 1.0507723064321002e-12, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 76, \"end\": 82, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin\", \"score\": 0.9999987864808277, \"rank\": 1.212583438145839e-06, \"text\": \"Dublin\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The civic reception, hosted by Dublin City Council, will take place at the GPO on O'Connell Street at 12.30pm.\", \"from\": 105, \"to\": 215, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 136, \"end\": 155, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin_City_Council\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.874186419479028e-36, \"text\": \"Dublin City Council\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q11204\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin_City_Council\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin_City_Council\"}, {\"begin\": 180, \"end\": 183, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_Post_Office\", \"score\": 0.9986390647598945, \"rank\": 0.0009630387818279678, \"text\": \"GPO\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_Post_Office\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_Post_Office\"}, {\"begin\": 187, \"end\": 203, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/O'Connell_Street\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.314513216191838e-41, \"text\": \"O'Connell Street\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/O'Connell_Street\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/O'Connell_Street\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team Ireland has won seven medals in Paris so far - four gold and three bronze - at its most successful Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 217, \"to\": 335, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 217, \"end\": 229, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999229203, \"rank\": 7.69257438597037e-11, \"text\": \"Team Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 254, \"end\": 259, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999786564333, \"rank\": 2.1343528533944818e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The event , which is planned in conjunction with the Olympic Federation of Ireland, will be free and open to all, with tickets not required.\", \"from\": 337, \"to\": 477, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have all enjoyed watching the Irish athletes do us proud in Paris,\\\" Lord Mayor of Dublin James Geoghegan said.\", \"from\": 479, \"to\": 593, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 513, \"end\": 518, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999956369642543, \"rank\": 4.345096103770583e-06, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 543, \"end\": 548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999786564333, \"rank\": 2.1343528533944818e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 565, \"end\": 571, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin\", \"score\": 0.9999987864808277, \"rank\": 1.212583438145839e-06, \"text\": \"Dublin\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin\"}, {\"begin\": 572, \"end\": 587, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Geoghegan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"James Geoghegan\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Geoghegan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Geoghegan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Now is our chance to tell them in person just how proud we are of them.\", \"from\": 595, \"to\": 667, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have no doubt their efforts will have inspired lots of girls and boys all over the city and country to try and be like them some day.\", \"from\": 668, \"to\": 803, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So come along to O'Connell St on Monday and let us give the Irish Team a welcome home to remember!\\\"\", \"from\": 805, \"to\": 905, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 866, \"end\": 871, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999956369642543, \"rank\": 4.345096103770583e-06, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team Ireland Chef de Mission Gavin Noble said: \\\"Over the past few weeks our athletes have performed outstandingly, and have inspired the nation with their endeavours at the Olympic Games in Paris.\", \"from\": 907, \"to\": 1103, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 907, \"end\": 919, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999229203, \"rank\": 7.69257438597037e-11, \"text\": \"Team Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 920, \"end\": 935, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Head_of_mission\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chef de Mission\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Head_of_mission\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Head_of_mission\"}, {\"begin\": 936, \"end\": 947, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gavin_Noble\", \"score\": 0.9999958127936122, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gavin Noble\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gavin_Noble\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gavin_Noble\"}, {\"begin\": 1097, \"end\": 1102, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999786564333, \"rank\": 2.1343528533944818e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are really proud of each and every one of them, and we would like to thank Dublin City Council for hosting such a special event to honour them.\\\"\", \"from\": 1105, \"to\": 1253, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1184, \"end\": 1203, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin_City_Council\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.874186419479028e-36, \"text\": \"Dublin City Council\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q11204\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin_City_Council\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin_City_Council\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Latest Paris 2024 stories  Dublin City Council is asking people to use public transport when travelling to and from the family-friendly, alcohol-free event and to enter O'Connell Street from the O'Connell Bridge end.\", \"from\": 1255, \"to\": 1471, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1282, \"end\": 1301, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin_City_Council\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.874186419479028e-36, \"text\": \"Dublin City Council\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q11204\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin_City_Council\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin_City_Council\"}, {\"begin\": 1424, \"end\": 1440, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/O'Connell_Street\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.314513216191838e-41, \"text\": \"O'Connell Street\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/O'Connell_Street\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/O'Connell_Street\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The event will have an impact on public transport.\", \"from\": 1473, \"to\": 1523, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Luas Green Line services will be suspended between Dominic and St Stephen's Green stops from 9.30am until 10pm to facilitate the homecoming.\", \"from\": 1525, \"to\": 1665, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1525, \"end\": 1540, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Green_Line_(Luas)\", \"score\": 0.9999999999979536, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Luas Green Line\", \"types\": [\"Q728937\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Green_Line_(Luas)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Green_Line_(Luas)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Luas Red Line trams will not operate between Smithfield and The Point stops from 9.30am to 10pm.\", \"from\": 1667, \"to\": 1763, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1727, \"end\": 1736, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Point_Theatre\", \"score\": 0.9999921230433853, \"rank\": 7.87701856671564e-06, \"text\": \"The Point\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Point_Theatre\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Point_Theatre\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bus services will be diverted from O'Connell Street from 10am and will recommence on the northbound side of the street at 5pm and on the southbound side at 10pm.\", \"from\": 1765, \"to\": 1926, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1800, \"end\": 1816, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/O'Connell_Street\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.314513216191838e-41, \"text\": \"O'Connell Street\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/O'Connell_Street\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/O'Connell_Street\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition to the reception, the Samuel Beckett Bridge across the River Liffey will feature a special message this Saturday and Sunday evening to celebrate Team Ireland's achievements.\", \"from\": 1928, \"to\": 2113, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1962, \"end\": 1983, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Beckett_Bridge\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Samuel Beckett Bridge\", \"types\": [\"Q12280\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Beckett_Bridge\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Beckett_Bridge\"}, {\"begin\": 2085, \"end\": 2097, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999229203, \"rank\": 7.69257438597037e-11, \"text\": \"Team Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a9 RT\\u00c9 2025.\", \"from\": 2117, \"to\": 2128, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"RT\\u00c9.ie is the website of Raidi\\u00f3 Teilif\\u00eds \\u00c9ireann, Ireland's National Public Service Media.\", \"from\": 2129, \"to\": 2219, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2154, \"end\": 2177, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"score\": 0.9993664851268295, \"rank\": 0.0006339164685885233, \"text\": \"Raidi\\u00f3 Teilif\\u00eds \\u00c9ireann\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\"}, {\"begin\": 2179, \"end\": 2186, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/R